Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是永久的实体障碍吗？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is it a permanent physical disability?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，不是{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是我无法爬那种太陡 或是到高处的楼梯{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It just means that I can't climb stairs that are too steep or go to high places,
