Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要喝一杯吗？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Would you like a drink now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，不用了 不，现在对我来说还太早{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, I don't think so. No, it's a little early in the day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么，这大概就是 所有的近况，是吧？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, I guess that just about covers everything, doesn't it?
