Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是个退休的警探 而你在造船业{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm a retired detective, and you're in the shipbuilding business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在想什么，盖文？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's on your mind, Gavin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我请你过来，史考特 也知道你辞掉警探工作{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I asked you to come up here, Scottie, knowing that you'd quit detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我想知道你愿不愿意重拾工作 帮我一个忙{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I wondered whether you'd go back on the job as a special favor to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请你跟踪我太太{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I want you to follow my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是那样的，我们婚姻很美满{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, it's not that. We're very happily married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么…{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我担心她会遭遇到危险{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm afraid some harm may come to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来自谁？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}已死的人{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Someone dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}史考特，你相信过去的人{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Scottie, do you believe that someone out of the past,
