Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:14:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我说这发生在 我太太身上，你怎么说？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I told you that I believe this has happened to my wife, what would you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会说带她去最近的 精神病医师，或心理医师{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, I'd say take her to the nearest psychiatrist, or psychologist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或神经科医师，或神经病 又或许就一般的家庭医师{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}or neurologist, or psycho... Or maybe just the plain family doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也会叫他检查你{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd have him check on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我找你就没用了 很抱歉浪费你的时间{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then you're of no use to me. I'm sorry I wasted your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}多谢你来，史考特{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thanks for coming in, Scottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我…我不想这么难堪{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I... I didn't mean to be that rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，这听起来很蠢，我知道{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, it sounds idiotic, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而你依然是那固执的苏格兰人 不是吗？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And you're still the hardheaded Scot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一直都是，你觉得我凭空捏造？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Always were. Do you think I'm making it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有凭空捏造 我不知道如何捏造{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not making it up. I wouldn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她会告诉我一些事{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She'll be talking to me about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}突然，说到一半就没了{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Suddenly, the words fade into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她眼睛会变得迷蒙 然后空无一物{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A cloud comes into her eyes and they go blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她到了别处，不再和我一起 成为我不认识的人{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She's somewhere else, away from me, someone I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我呼唤她，她根本听不到{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I call to her, she doesn't even hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后，长叹一声后，她回来了{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then, with a long sigh, she's back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有神地看着我 甚至不知道自己出神过{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}looks at me brightly, doesn't even know she's been away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}无法告诉我是何时或何地{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Can't tell me where or when.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么，这多常发生？{\r}\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, how often does this happen?
